  "detailed_description": "<strong>Become a DragonRider!</strong><br>Immerse yourself in 10 fantasy worlds and even explore the deep sea if you dare. DragonRideVR is suitable for all ages!<br><u><strong>Game Modes and Features</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/85896172fa6f0ab2eb7e8980d1652087.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span> <br>Hop on the back of a dragon for a pre-set ride! Choose from various modes including flying, walking, swimming, and even underwater diving! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/f737fd51625923e4399834fc2685d7ae.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Take in the beauty of the different worlds in a stationary panoramic view mode. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/b0c3aea361b25c79c330e86059a369ee.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Experience breathtaking worlds swinging your swords to the musical beats. Pop the balloons and break the targets as you fly towards them on the back of the dragon! Match up the color and direction to get maximum points! <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>25 Handcrafted songs each with 5 difficulty levels.<br></li><li>Global Leaderboards.<br></li><li>5 Ride Types from smooth straight to more challenging wild! Progress and unlock custom options.<br></li><li>Easy to play and a great workout.<br></li><li>Custom song support.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/c5729f0a5e249e6f721bb52d10935da9.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot targets and balloons on the back of a dragon, Choose Laps or Time Challenge!<br></li><li>Skill shots and long shots are rewarded!<br></li><li>Automatically activate magic spells (while they last) to help improve your score! Find the 9 Power-up spells within the game.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/4a5c3bb23882f7fb466bf33e4f4a3b0e.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Using your motion controllers you fly the dragon - you can customize the controls to how you like to fly. Explore the magical worlds on your terms. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/b9f869ac38e2c10eec842748e9838c34.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Find the lost dragon eggs before time runs out!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/aaba90de958d2d732f15e19a4cc72fdd.webp?t=1646935985\" width=188 height=45 /></span><br>Pop balloons to get as many points as possible!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Become a DragonRider!</strong><br>Immerse yourself in 10 fantasy worlds and even explore the deep sea if you dare. DragonRideVR is suitable for all ages!<br><u><strong>Game Modes and Features</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/85896172fa6f0ab2eb7e8980d1652087.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span> <br>Hop on the back of a dragon for a pre-set ride! Choose from various modes including flying, walking, swimming, and even underwater diving! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/f737fd51625923e4399834fc2685d7ae.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Take in the beauty of the different worlds in a stationary panoramic view mode. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/b0c3aea361b25c79c330e86059a369ee.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Experience breathtaking worlds swinging your swords to the musical beats. Pop the balloons and break the targets as you fly towards them on the back of the dragon! Match up the color and direction to get maximum points! <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>25 Handcrafted songs each with 5 difficulty levels.<br></li><li>Global Leaderboards.<br></li><li>5 Ride Types from smooth straight to more challenging wild! Progress and unlock custom options.<br></li><li>Easy to play and a great workout.<br></li><li>Custom song support.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/c5729f0a5e249e6f721bb52d10935da9.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot targets and balloons on the back of a dragon, Choose Laps or Time Challenge!<br></li><li>Skill shots and long shots are rewarded!<br></li><li>Automatically activate magic spells (while they last) to help improve your score! Find the 9 Power-up spells within the game.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/4a5c3bb23882f7fb466bf33e4f4a3b0e.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Using your motion controllers you fly the dragon - you can customize the controls to how you like to fly. Explore the magical worlds on your terms. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/b9f869ac38e2c10eec842748e9838c34.webp?t=1646935985\" width=150 height=36 /></span><br>Find the lost dragon eggs before time runs out!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1197620/extras/aaba90de958d2d732f15e19a4cc72fdd.webp?t=1646935985\" width=188 height=45 /></span><br>Pop balloons to get as many points as possible!",
